column5: Fishing LOTW, Big Narrows area next week. Any helpful suggestions re walleyes, northerns and smallies? Any idea on water temperature and Spring so far up there? Thanks.
If you don't get an answer at Walleye Central I suggest you try the question here http://www.justfishontario.com/
Water temps are down, really late start this season.Talked to few guys who said fishing was fair, but nothing to write home about.Hopefully weather will warm up and get things going.D'arcy
